        <div type="translation">
            <ab>P. L. Bat. 25 26

                    Stotoetis, son of Harpagathes, grandson of Harpagathes, to Diogas, greetings. I acknowledge having receive from you as a loan two hundred silver drachmas, tot. dr. 200, which I shall repay whenever it be required. If I should not repay according to what has been written, I shall pay as a fine - - -.</ab>
